37611>>>>>    Procedure OnNavigateForward tWebNavigateData NavigateData Integer hoInvokingView Integer hoInvokingObject
37614>>>>>        Case Begin
37614>>>>>            Case (NavigateData.eNavigateType = nfFromMain)
